Cards Against Huge Manatees
Project Synergy
Python 3.5.1
Requires python-telegram-bot library and pydblite
Python-Telegram-Bot library: https://github.com/python-telegram-bot/python-telegram-bot

Installation instructions:
From the command line run:
pip install python-telegram-bot
pip install pydblite

Download the source code and extract to a directory

From the command line run:
cd 'yourExtractedDirectory'
python ./cahm.py

IMPORTANT!!!
Please note that the sleep threshold in cahm.py may have to be adjusted to avoid
going over the Telegram API message limit. The limit is about one message per
second and not more than 20 messages per minute to the same group.